                <hr style="text-align: center; position: relative; left: -20%; width: 1000%; border-color:#dddddd; top: 8px; z-index: 8;" />
                <p id="sffll" style="position: relative; z-index: 99;">&copy;@DateTime.Now.Year - StoreFront</p>
